  ('self', 'cc-similarweb', E'SimilarWeb Data API', E'> Free SimilarWeb data endpoint - gotchas, rate limits, proxy requirements, data structure

## Free Data Endpoint

```
GET https://data.similarweb.com/api/v1/data?domain={domain}
```

**No API key needed** - public endpoint, but heavily protected.

## Required Headers (MUST have all)

```
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36...
Accept: application/json, text/plain, */*
Accept-Language: en-US,en;q=0.9
Referer: https://www.similarweb.com/
```

Without `User-Agent` + `Referer` → **403 Forbidden**. Rotate User-Agents.

## Proxy Required

Direct IP gets blocked fast. Must use residential proxy (datacenter IPs blocked).

```bash
# Working example (Webshare residential-rotate)
curl -x "http://USER-residential-rotate:PASS@p.webshare.io:80" \\
  -H "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0..." -H "Referer: https://www.similarweb.com/" \\
  "https://data.similarweb.com/api/v1/data?domain=example.com"
```

### Axios gotcha
`axios` with `proxy` config causes SSL errors on HTTPS targets via HTTP proxy. Use one of:
- `curl` via `execSync` (most reliable)
- `https-proxy-agent` package with `httpsAgent` + `proxy: false`

## Data Update Frequency

- **Monthly only** - SimilarWeb updates data once per month
- No point refreshing same domain within 25 days
- `Engagments.Month` and `Engagments.Year` tell which month\'s data it is

## Response Structure (key fields)

```json
{
  "SiteName": "example.com",
  "Engagments": {
    "Visits": "144430714",      // STRING not number!
    "BounceRate": "0.369...",   // STRING
    "PagePerVisit": "4.466...", // STRING
    "TimeOnSite": "273.81...",  // STRING
    "Month": "3",
    "Year": "2026"
  },
  "GlobalRank": { "Rank": 278 },           // number
  "CountryRank": { "Country": 704, "Rank": 6 }, // Rank is country rank, Country is code
  "CategoryRank": { "Rank": "1", "Category": "News_and_Media" }, // Rank is STRING
  "TrafficSources": {
    "Social": 0.031,       // numbers (0-1 fractions)
    "Paid Referrals": 0.005,
    "Mail": 0.0003,
    "Referrals": 0.033,
    "Search": 0.328,
    "Direct": 0.601
  },
  "TopCountryShares": [
    { "Country": 704, "CountryCode": "VN", "Value": 0.852 }  // top 5
  ],
  "EstimatedMonthlyVisits": {
    "2026-01-01": 131367922,  // last 3 months, numbers
    "2026-02-01": 109443905,
    "2026-03-01": 144430714
  },
  "TopKeywords": [
    { "Name": "keyword", "EstimatedValue": 2391720, "Volume": 495320, "Cpc": 1.18 }
  ],
  "AiTrafficDetails": {        // NEW - AI chatbot referral data
    "Traffic": {
      "Split": [
        { "Name": "chatgpt.com", "Rank": 1 },
        { "Name": "gemini.google.com", "Rank": 2 }
      ]
    },
    "TotalVisits": 153593
  },
  "Category": "news_and_media",
  "IsSmall": false,            // boolean
  "Countries": [...]           // HUGE array of all countries - filter out when storing
}
```

## Gotchas

1. **Engagments fields are STRINGS** - must `parseFloat()` before storing
2. **CategoryRank.Rank is STRING** - must `parseInt()`
3. **Countries array is 250+ items** - reference data, don\'t store per-domain
4. **Engagments typo** - it\'s "Engagments" not "Engagements" (SW\'s typo)
5. **No data for small sites** - returns minimal response with `IsSmall: true` and empty metrics
6. **Rate limiting** - 429 after ~50 requests from same IP. Back off 5-15 min
7. **403 blocked** - IP banned, switch proxy. Cool down 30+ min

## Anti-Detection Best Practices

- Random delay 3-8s between requests
- Rotate User-Agent from pool of 3-5
- Max ~5,000 req/day spread over 17 hours (6AM-11PM)
- Residential proxy only (Webshare, IPRoyal, Bright Data)
- Never burst >10 req/min sustained

## Dripfeed Strategy (for refreshing large datasets)

- Top 100K domains only (covers 95%+ of user queries)
- ~3,300 req/day = 100K / 30 days
- Priority: top 1K (weekly) > top 10K (biweekly) > rest (monthly)
- Skip domains updated <25 days ago
- On-demand fetch for long-tail (not in top 100K)
